name: Barbie Careers Doll & Playset
description: Explore a world of creative play and storytelling fun with the Barbie Baby Doctor Playset! Makes a great gift for kids 3 years old and up, especially those interested in medicine and caretaking! Doll cannot stand alone.

name: Barbie Careers Brunette Dentist
description: Dressed in her white coat, Barbie Dentist doll is ready to take care of her adorable toddler patient. Kids can role-play as both doctor and patient for storytelling fun! The doll and accessory set makes a great gift for kids 3 years and older, especially those who dream of being in the medical field.

name: Barbie Skipper Babysitters
description: Play out classic babysitting moments with Barbie Skipper Babysitters Inc. dolls and playsets!This Skipper Babysitters Inc. playset features Skipper babysitter doll, a baby doll and a stroller that bounces up and down as it's pushed Inspire nurturing play and realistic storytelling with accessories.

name: Skipper Babysitters
description: Fill the pink whale-shaped squirt toy with ice-cold water and spray to activate the color change or cool off Skipper doll, too! Skipper babysitter doll wears a swimsuit with trendy tropical print, cover-up and sunglasses. A colorful floatie and two drinks add additional inspiration for storytelling, plus plug-and-play design holds them in place for playtime action and easy cleanup.

Pat her head and she’ll call you Momma Realistic baby doll with lifelike baby powder fresh scent, cuddly body, silky hair, open/close eyes Nurturing play: Dress baby in her removable outfit and perfectly packaged for a gift
